"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"有 新都城"},{"pid":"8df7db50896caac5e2c4e775124bcd8434ef2aed","tid":911230,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T00:50:03.000Z","msg":"支那狗集中地"},{"pid":"93e140dc9d15501ad4fd9fd7f8ba0fba937cb00e","tid":911230,"uid":48579,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"14d66bb106bdf09c1c3ee5ffe14fcf94163a1975","tid":911230,"uid":119022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"商場都無個叫一應俱全<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"你肯定唔係住開北角 <br />\n就咁計區內商場 <br />\n健威有健威坊 隔離有港運城<br />\n過少少又有新都城 和富商場 <br />\n城市花園有城市金庫 國都商場<br />\n炮台山個邊有柏麗大道英皇商場賣game <br />\n夠哂日常市民需求<br />\n<br />\n加上北角地理位置良好 <br />\n左鄰銅鑼灣 右近太古吉之島 <br />\n要去各大型商場 坐叮叮都係廿分鐘之內嘅事<br />\n根本無必要係北角起大商場<br />\n所以話北角無商場真係on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772d56638b42535a4bfc7abfff71db2b91f1bc0c","tid":911230,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T05:11:37.000Z","msg":"福建賤種聚居地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}